#: ../iot/homeassistant/home_assistant.rst:7
msgid ""
"Home Assistant is a Python-based open source smart home system that "
"supports smart home devices of many brands and can easily implement voice"
" control and automation of the devices. You can run Home-assistant on the"
" Raspberry Pi, without having to send your data out onto the internet. "
"This means that you have total control over your data, limit the amount "
"of internet traffic from your smart devices, and tighten up security."
msgstr ""

#: ../iot/homeassistant/home_assistant.rst:13
msgid ""
